In the empirical analysis, we need to change the description of needs so
 that it is decomposed into a component that varies proportional to the
 members of the family and one that moves with the assets acquired by the
 consumer.
 The estimation of 
\begin_inset Formula $mA_{t}^{\alpha}$
\end_inset

 could thus be together with the price of needs.
 
\end_layout

